{"type":"message","id":"0e272f5b","parentId":"717580e6","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:28:04.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both web searches failed due to authentication issues, and both web fetches were blocked. I have no viable way to get current news. I need to clearly state this limitation rather than fabricating content."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n**科技新闻简报 · 2026年3月28日**\n\n⚠️ **无法生成简报的原因**\n\n本次简报请求因以下限制无法完成：\n\n1. **搜索 API 认证失败**：Kimi web search 返回 401 Invalid Authentication，当前配置的 API 密钥无效或已过期。\n2. **网页抓取被屏蔽**：Hacker News 和 The Verge 均解析为内部/特殊用途 IP 地址，无法抓取。\n\n---\n\n**当前状态**\n\n作为研究型 Agent，我的职责是返回事实而非猜测。在无法获取真实信息源的情况下，生成\"新闻简报\"只会产出虚构内容，这违背了**避免营销口吻、优先可信来源**的核心要求。\n\n---\n\n**建议的下一步**\n\n1. 检查 OpenClaw 的 `web_search` 配置（Kimi API Key），确认是否有效。\n2. 更换为可用的网页内容源（如配置代理或使用其他可访问的新闻站点）。\n3. 或者手动提供几条新闻线索，我可以帮助改写和格式化。\n\n如需我尝试其他方式获取信息，请告知具体方案。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774711674367,"responseId":"06172679a619da61705c7c2b1d6e64fc"}}
